---
title: Hummus & Cucumber Salad Pita Pockets with Red Pepper Spread, Feta & Creamy Dill Sauce
description: If you ask us, the pita is the ultimate pocket: You can stuff just about anything in it and if it overflows that means you stuffed it right. These pita pockets are just one example. You’ll fill the pita with a fresh cucumber and tomato salad, a swipe of hummus, a creamy and tangy dill dressing, feta, and as much hot sauce as your taste buds desire. When you’re ready to eat, don’t let any dripping sauce or salad go to waste—that’s what your fingers are for!
